trans-unit.source: Provides minimal design-time support for <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager" /> controls.
trans-unit.target: Proporciona la compatibilidad mínima en tiempo de diseño para los controles <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager" />.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerDesigner> class provides a bare-minimum design-time rendering of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerDesigner> clase proporciona una representación en tiempo de diseño mínima de la <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control.

trans-unit.source: It appears on the design surface as a plain gray box showing the name of the class and the ID of the current <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>.
trans-unit.target: Aparece en la superficie de diseño como un cuadro gris sin formato que muestra el nombre de la clase y el identificador del elemento actual <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>.

trans-unit.source: You can change the rendering of a custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control by overriding the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A> method in the same manner as with any standard <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>.
trans-unit.target: Puede cambiar la representación de un personalizado <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control invalidando el <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A> método en la misma manera que con cualquier estándar <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.ControlDesigner>.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> property is overridden to always return `true`.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerDesigner.UsePreviewControl%2A> propiedad se reemplaza para que siempre devuelva `true`.

trans-unit.source: The following code example shows how to change the design-time appearance of a custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control by overriding the <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A> method of the designer.
trans-unit.target: En el ejemplo de código siguiente se muestra cómo cambiar la apariencia en tiempo de diseño personalizado <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control invalidando el <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerDesigner.GetDesignTimeHtml%2A> método del diseñador.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerDesigner" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa una nueva instancia de la clase <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.Design.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManagerDesigner" />.

trans-unit.source: Returns an empty string (""), which indicates that the visual design environment should revert to default control rendering.
trans-unit.target: Devuelve una cadena vacía (""), que indica que el entorno de diseño visual debería revertirse a la representación predeterminada del control.

trans-unit.source: The <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager" /> control associated with the designer.
Binds the designer to the associated <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager" /> control.
trans-unit.target: Enlaza el diseñador al control <see cref="T:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager" /> asociado.

trans-unit.source: Gets a value indicating whether the designer should use a temporary copy rather than the actual control associated with the designer to generate the design-time markup.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene un valor que indica si el diseñador debe usar una copia temporal, en lugar del control real que está asociado al diseñador, para generar el marcado en tiempo de diseño.
